  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 10th level, you learn to make use of the Medical tools you have access to, in order to better utilize them to help an injured ally. Your skill with the Medicine Kit has accelerated to compensate for your lack of Medical Ninjutsu. Your new found skills are expressed in the following ways;</p><ul><li><p><strong>Medical Check Up</strong>: You reduce the time spent down to 1 minute.</p></li><li><p><strong>Light Patch up</strong>: You increase the die size to a d6.</p></li><li><p><strong>Condition Treatment</strong>: The die used is changed from a d6 into 2d4.</p></li><li><p><strong>Blood Pill Creation</strong>: You can create two pills per kit before spending any charges.</p></li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
